Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["\<\
Exercise 1. Importance of depth in ANNs to approximate functions.\
\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.825880286289219*^9, 3.8258803189786243`*^9}, {
  3.825881111356182*^9, 
  3.8258811434065046`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"51d72cd4-3b27-453c-b16c-\
3b8bb1e6e539"],

Cell["\<\
The universal approximation theorem introduced in lectures shows that a \
linear layer followed by an activation function layer (i.e. a linear \
combination of activation functions) can accurately approximate any function \
if the layer is wide enough. According to this result, deep ANNs (i.e. ANNs \
with several layers) are not needed to approximate functions. In practice, \
however, the number of parameters required to approximate a certain function \
decreases if the depth of the ANN increases. This is an important motivation \
to use deep neural networks as opposed to shallow ANNs with a wide layer.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.821023336737196*^9, 3.8210234057645307`*^9}, {
  3.821023450775815*^9, 3.8210234621102567`*^9}, {3.8210235401052704`*^9, 
  3.821023560062215*^9}, {3.821023672112166*^9, 3.8210238021579666`*^9}, {
  3.8210244777277827`*^9, 3.8210246615293927`*^9}, {3.8210247251879354`*^9, 
  3.8210247521410446`*^9}, {3.821024809906029*^9, 3.821024932592491*^9}, {
  3.8210249953669877`*^9, 3.8210250515960093`*^9}, {3.821025605797887*^9, 
  3.821025745281686*^9}, {3.8210257935328455`*^9, 3.821025826383957*^9}, {
  3.8258804559959316`*^9, 3.825880463691436*^9}, {3.8258805256553802`*^9, 
  3.825880587415537*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1def0f64-e999-4115-bc2e-\
6ba178ea60c6"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Task 1", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.825946518177785*^9, 
  3.8259465194574137`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1deb6920-4344-4512-bc02-\
3af664d15bfa"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Follow the methods used in lecture\[CloseCurlyQuote]s section on the \
universal approximation theorem to generate data for the function ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"f", "(", "x", ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Cos", "(", "x", ")"}], " ", 
     SuperscriptBox["e", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"-", "x"}], "/", "10"}]]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8e9e13e6-286b-4be3-8f5f-63ee88afa047"],
 " obtained by sampling ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"N", "=", "5000"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1cb0852a-ea6f-4cd5-9c8b-ac2137ae863e"],
 " values of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["x", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e5aefbdd-67c9-4dbc-b56e-2a4394733a0a"],
 " in the interval ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"[", 
    RowBox[{"0", ",", "12"}], "]"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9e02b19f-33f8-4b1c-92e6-fa5a1558aab9"],
 ". Plot the data points ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"(", 
      RowBox[{
       SubscriptBox["x", "i"], ",", 
       RowBox[{"f", "(", 
        SubscriptBox["x", "i"], ")"}]}], ")"}], ",", 
     RowBox[{"i", "=", "1"}], ",", "...", ",", "N"}], "}"}], 
   TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->"afd11b71-b0ba-4cb4-8f44-ae46d476ac53"],
 " in a scatterplot. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8210264233611374`*^9, 3.8210265404551134`*^9}, {
  3.8210265742916403`*^9, 3.821026681910787*^9}, {3.8258806694621525`*^9, 
  3.825880689975082*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"686bce1b-904f-49c5-ba9b-\
b15f1cb8f208"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Task 2", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.825946509276843*^9, 
  3.8259465108569975`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1ba085ef-5534-4c95-8d10-\
7455d8f7a889"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In this task, you will train ANNs to approximate the function ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"f", "(", "x", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9dee6d99-210c-41db-9397-ab2b3cffe48c"],
 ". In particular, build three neural networks, ANN1, ANN2 and ANN3 \
consisting of linear layers followed by logistic sigmoid elementwise layers \
of decreasing width and increasing depth, as shown by the following summary \
graphics:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.821027018435912*^9, 3.8210272057636395`*^9}, {
  3.8210273360349126`*^9, 3.8210275038349295`*^9}, {3.8210277705291767`*^9, 
  3.821027776778466*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"99c4fd3f-d12b-41de-91aa-\
b88bf69fe728"],

