 "\n\nMore explicitly, this can be obtained with NetChain and the appropriate \
layers as follows (I refer to the layer as ",
 StyleBox["logisticClass", "CodeText"],
 "):\n\nlogisticClass = \
NetChain[{LAYERS},\"Output\"\[Rule]NetDecoder[{\"Class\",{\"A\",\"B\"}}]]"
}], "Text",
