 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8258794176105537`*^9, 
  3.8258794204083443`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"64449235-3a41-470c-b0a4-\
0d9287e6d059"],

Cell["\<\
Non-linear activation functions such LogisticSigmoid, Tanh and Ramp described \
in lectures are at the core of the success of ANNs. Indeed, non-linear \
activation functions allow ANNs to be applied to complex datasets that cannot \
be dealt with by only using linear layers. For example, ANNs involving linear \
layers would be able to classify elements into two classes A and B in the \
following dataset:\
\>", "Text",
