Cell["\<\
Build a neural net to classify points into classes A and B with a linear \
layer followed by a SoftmaxLayer and a class net decoder to transform the \
output of the SoftmaxLayer into classes A and B, as described in section \
11.8.3. The ANN should have the following architecture:\
